{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784387093025,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97fffeEAeDNR9iyiwCDi","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_txES3smKc2jO3BMjw6efGkeh","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-review","description":"Review security dimension","prompt":"Execute exactly one command-owned deep-review LEAF iteration from `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/review/lineages/sol-b/prompts/iteration-2.md`. Read the rendered prompt and current externalized state first. Stay read-only on the target and write only the four allowed lineage paths named in the prompt. Produce narrative, one canonical state-log append, matching delta, and strategy update. No sub-agents. Verify exact final verdict line, route proof, v2 graphless ledger, and output consistency before returning.","command":"/deep:review"},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08a457922ffeLOx1oSwIOZs2Xn\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Review Iteration 2 Complete\n\n- **Focus:** Security trust boundaries\n- **Findings:** 3 total — P0: 0, P1: 3, P2: 0\n- **newFindingsRatio:** 0.60\n- **Dimensions completed:** Correctness, Security\n- **Remaining:** Traceability, Maintainability\n- **Edge cases:** Planned contracts only; no active runtime exploit. Code graph unavailable.\n- **Integration evidence:** No runtime implementation claimed.\n- **Next focus:** Traceability\n\nVerified:\n- Final line: `Review verdict: CONDITIONAL`\n- Canonical state append matches delta first record\n- Route proof valid\n- Complete v2 graphless ledger present\n- Narrative, strategy, state, and delta are consistent\n\n**Files written:**\n- `iterations/iteration-002.md`\n- `deep-review-state.jsonl` — one append\n- `deltas/iter-002.jsonl`\n- `deep-review-strategy.md`\n\n**Status:** `complete`\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08a55b97fffeEAeDNR9iyiwCDi","sessionId":"ses_08a457922ffeLOx1oSwIOZs2Xn","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated